{
  "page": "Broken Shield",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Broken Shield</b> inn is one of three inns in the market town of <a href=\"/index.php/Weeping_Town\" title=\"Weeping Town\">Weeping Town</a> which lies on the southern shore of <a href=\"/index.php/Cape_Wrath\" title=\"Cape Wrath\">Cape Wrath</a>.  It has a common room. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>After Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> and her party disembark from the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Peregrine\" title=\"Peregrine\">Peregrine</a></i> at Weeping Town Arianne sends Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a> to the Broken Shield in order to gather intelligence, as she knows its common room is rife with rumors. \n</p><p>In the Broken Shield, Ser Daemon is told that the great <a href=\"/index.php/Septry\" title=\"Septry\">septry</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Holf_of_Men&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Holf of Men (page does not exist)\">Holf of Men</a> has been burned and looted by raiders from the sea, and a hundred young novices from the motherhouse on <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden_Isle\" title=\"Maiden Isle\">Maiden Isle</a> were carried off into <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slavery</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>That night, Arianne dispatches the first of her <a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">ravens</a> back to <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, reporting to <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">her father</a> on all they'd seen and heard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ar2-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_II_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403155539\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.018 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 86/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 475/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1880/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 471/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 474/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.097      1 -total\n 43.65%    2.661      1 Template:Warning/twow\n 34.18%    2.084      1 Template:References\n 33.36%    2.034      1 Template:Warning\n 22.50%    1.372      1 Template:Mbox\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:22277-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403155539 and revision id 241361\n -->\n",
